songs.title: Roller Dirby
songs.lyrics:
Pin up girls at the roller derby
Take me down to Newark, New Jersey

American flags; blue, blue streamers
Everybody's laughing, the crowd is screaming

I used to think I was the Maharaja
Ah, oh

Baby, I've become someone
Baby, I've become
Baby, I've become someone

Not of this world, hey, yeah, yeah
Not of this world, hey, yeah, yeah
